{"tid":2035847,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"食M記同幫襯Starbucks/黃店有咩野問題，黃色經濟圈可以搞到支爆","createTime":"2020-05-26T06:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T03:54:47.000Z","uid":61161,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"594ae05d695a9765d8c36508b8f7cadd63d03d5a","tid":2035847,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:39:27.000Z","msg":"問題係你嘅錢去咗邊啲人身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當M記同華潤合資，華潤佔3成股份，你俾$10食M記，$7會落M記袋，$3會落入華潤手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你俾$20去食吉野家，就$20都係藍營嘅人賺<br />\n如果你俾$20幫襯黃店，就$20都係自己人身上獲益再可能有其他用途/幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外資奶共做生意<br />\n其實唔應該反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Starbucks/M記/Apple Store係賺走緊大陸人錢<br />\n<br />\n最好100%俾返錢黃店賺就梗係好，但如果你係學生好窮，好有需要食M記，同路人希望可以屌少啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買咖啡黎講，大把黃店/中立無表態外資咖啡店 e.g. Blue Bottle/%<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，唔洗定到門檻好高，改變下習慣就可以了，謹記唔好幫襯藍店就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想支爆其實唔係大家想像中咁難，中國錢塘水滾塘魚，外資賺大陸人錢，中資賺唔到外資，最後就會支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支爆後，中共就會解體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港就可以變獨立個體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28248559c4277baae9f65e1c5c7f2d9fbe35999","tid":2035847,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:42:00.000Z","msg":"其實蕭生都做到出晒面啦<br />\n<br />\n又餐廳又超市<br />\n<br />\n睇你地有冇心做者<br />\n<br />\n每日堅持行半個鐘食時代"},{"pid":"a430b70b18d255d925aab1972d0ce3e1fb69c6a9","tid":2035847,"uid":35365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:43:06.000Z","msg":"%你講緊arabica?<br />\n紅底架"},{"pid":"e3167417f29dac9e89508e92f1c5fc5d8721087a","tid":2035847,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":